data.description: Looking for a single story in a wonderful location? A home with fully paid off solar panels? Four bedrooms? A conveniently split floor plan with a very spacious master and a closet to die for? You just found it! Upon entry, you'll be greeted by the formal living room perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet moments. The heart of the home is the large family room which seamlessly flows into the open kitchen. The spacious kitchen is featuring ample counter space, and a large convenient breakfast area. Step outside to a covered back patio perfect for outdoor activities and gardening.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home.
